H. No. 3192 / 57 OG No. 7, 1191 (February 13, 1961)

[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 2795, June 19, 1960 ]

AN ACT CREATING CERTAIN BARRIOS IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF TUAO, PROVINCE OF CAGAYAN.

Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:

SECTION 1. The following sitios in the Municipality of Tuao, Province of Cagayan, are converted into barrios of said municipality, to wit:

Sitio Pata to Barrio Pata;

Sitio Dagupan to Barrio Dagupan;

Sitio Palca to Barrio Palca;

Sitio Naruangan to Barrio Naruangan;

Sitio Bugnay to Barrio Bugnay;

Sitio San Juan to Barrio San Juan;

Sitio Moleg to Barrio Moleg;

Sitio Taribugu to Barrio Taribugu;

Sitio Culung to Barrio Culung;

Sitio Bicok to Barrio Bicok;

Sitio Talia to Barrio Talia;

Sitio Malummin to Barrio Malummin;

Sitio Gurengad to Barrio Gurengad;

Sitio Angang to Barrio Angang; and

Sitio Lalambini to Barrio Lalambini.

SEC. 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.

Enacted without Executive approval, June 19, 1960.
